<i>adverb</i>: 시름시름 [시름시름] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>시름시름 [시름시름]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lingeringly</dd><br>
<dd>병이 더 심해지지도 않고 나아지지 않으면서 오랫동안 계속 아픈 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one suffers from an illness for a long time while the illness gets neither worse nor better.</dd><br>
<dd>2. (no equivalent expression)</dd><br>
<dd>비나 눈 등이 조용히 계속해서 내리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of rain or snow falling quietly and continuously.</dd><br>
<dd>3. feebly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 조용하거나 힘없이 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of moving very quietly or weakly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>